    "asOf": "2020-03-23",
    "date": "2020-04-15T13:26:28Z",
    "text": "Increasing Hospital Capacity to Fight the Coronavirus Act of 2020\n\nThis bill allows unapproved capital expenses that are made by health care facilities during the public health emergency declared on January 31, 2020, relating to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) to be included in federal payment determinations under Medicare and Medicaid."
